00:12:17.480 --> 00:12:20.510 align:middle line:84%
>> There's a human propensity
for the mind to consistently

00:12:20.510 --> 00:12:22.550 align:middle line:90%
move back to the past.

00:12:22.550 --> 00:12:24.260 align:middle line:84%
That's a natural
mechanism that's

00:12:24.260 --> 00:12:26.540 align:middle line:90%
been developed over eons.

00:12:26.540 --> 00:12:31.700 align:middle line:84%
