00:13:39.470 --> 00:13:42.180 align:middle line:90%
become the means of thinking.

00:13:42.180 --> 00:13:46.100 align:middle line:84%
In other words, feelings
determine their thinking.

00:13:46.100 --> 00:13:49.190 align:middle line:84%
When that happens, we only
are living from the past,

00:13:49.190 --> 00:13:51.800 align:middle line:84%
because by definition,
feelings are

00:13:51.800 --> 00:13:54.660 align:middle line:90%
associated to some past event.

00:13:54.660 --> 00:13:56.660 align:middle line:84%
So if we determine
our future based

00:13:56.660 --> 00:13:58.370 align:middle line:84%
on a feeling, what
we're really saying

00:13:58.370 --> 00:14:01.640 align:middle line:84%
is I'm trying to create
a future situation

00:14:01.640 --> 00:14:03.350 align:middle line:90%
from a past situation.

00:14:03.350 --> 00:14:07.430 align:middle line:84%
And invariably, we will
always continuously recreate

00:14:07.430 --> 00:14:08.990 align:middle line:90%
the future based on the past.

00:14:08.990 --> 00:14:11.640 align:middle line:84%
And that future will
be more of the past.

00:14:11.640 --> 00:14:13.670 align:middle line:90%
