00:14:15.590 --> 00:14:18.320 align:middle line:84%
people who are
wired in suffering,

00:14:18.320 --> 00:14:21.560 align:middle line:84%
people who are wired
in their insecurity.

00:14:21.560 --> 00:14:25.200 align:middle line:84%
And the feelings become the
barometer of their reality.

00:14:25.200 --> 00:14:28.070 align:middle line:84%
Then in their future
experience, they

00:14:28.070 --> 00:14:32.180 align:middle line:84%
